column2: SELECT s.specObjID, g.class, g.subClass, x.z, x.ra, x.dec, x.plate, x.fiberID, x.MJD, s.oii_#_flux as OII3#, s.oiii_#_flux as OIII4#, s.oiii_#_flux as OIII5#, s.h_beta_flux as HBeta, s.h_alpha_flux as HAlpha, s.nii_#_flux as NII6#, x.logMass as logM FROM galSpecLine s JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranNoDust x ON x.specObjID = s.specObjID JOIN specObj g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE x.plate = # AND x.fiberID = #
